  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd\u2019 \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9c\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 'people' development budget is coming",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Secretary Vajira Abeywardhana said that President Ranil Wickremesinghe will present a budget plan that will give priority to the development of poor people and develop the people with tax reforms.",
        "In connection with the 76th anniversary of the United National Party, he said the above in his address at a meeting held in Galle.",
        "He also pointed out that this will not be a budget for the construction of roads and buildings, but a budget that can provide food and clothes to the poor people who are without food and clothing.",
        "He said that a generation of malnourished children is being born and as a solution to those problems, the President will present a People Development Budget along with tax reforms.",
        "He said that he hoped that the hunger of the children suffering from this would be alleviated and steps would be taken to correct the mistakes made by the previous government.",
        "He said that anyone can have dreams of becoming Prime Minister and President and said that they should also have a plan to make 2 million people live."
      ],
